snippet.title: DEADCAM | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
DEADCAM is an 80's & 90's inspired analog-survival-horror game based around found-footage and built in Unreal Engine 5. Explore and survive various "recordings" set in unique settings and locations.
Wishlist here: playdeadcam.com
